---
title: Crumbed Banana Blossom with Spiced Wedges, Rainbow Slaw & Plant-Based Aioli
description: This versatile fruit with a similar texture to cooked white fish is the perfect plant-based alternative to switch out with your regular
protein. Pair it with a crunchy rainbow slaw and spiced wedges, and it's just like a plate from a Southern cookout.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crumbed-banana-blossom-c9c150b7.jpg
